The UK Intelligence Community's Design System This Design System helps you to design and build complex, specialised apps and services. It's used by MI6, MI5, GCHQ, HMGCC, our national security partner, and our additional partners to construct tools that keep the UK safe and prosperous. The Design System empowers through accessibility-by-design, a diverse and inclusive community, and flexible tech and implementation options. To find out more, delve into our story on how we support people and organisations develop valuable apps and services accessible for everyone. Read our story
For designers Whether you're building a new interface or refining an existing one, our Figma UI Kit, principles and documentation enable you to create intuitive, consistent and accessible designs with ease.
Explore design Read our design principles
For developers Our development UI Kit is built with Stencil.js to ensure seamless integration across React, Vue, Angular and other frameworks. With a focus on accessibility and ease of use, these components equip developers to create responsive and inclusive experiences.
Explore development Learn how we test components

Contribute to our community

The Design System is primarily built for the large numbers of apps and services we have. While most of the work is undertaken by our Engineering teams, we've open sourced our Design System for the world to see, use and contribute to (which we think is very cool). Find out more
